      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "given him of Paul",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] He had heard the Apostle speak of the contributions which he had gathered for the Jews in Jerusalem. His thought would naturally be that if he could raise money for the needs of others, he could do so for his own release.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
